# ZMK-editor devshell — Node + pnpm, no Rust toolchain. Reuses the
# root flake's `web` shell (identical toolchain: Node + pnpm). No
# per-subdirectory flake exists — kobu has one source of truth at the
# repo root (two levels up: web/zmk-editor → kobu). `watch_file` reloads
# this shell when the root flake or its lockfile changes.
watch_file ../../flake.nix ../../flake.lock
use flake "path:../..#web"
